[SN]TITLE[SN]
Yohan Benalouane: Leicester defender joins Fiorentina on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Fiorentina have signed Leicester City defender Yohan Benalouane on loan until the end of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
France-born Benalouane, 28, signed a four-year deal when he joined the Foxes in August from Italian side Atalanta.
He is yet to start a top-flight game for the Premier League leaders.
Fiorentina are managed by former Leicester boss Paulo Sousa and are third in the Serie A table, eight points behind leaders Napoli with 16 matches remaining.
